    <item>
      <title>布林肯在新的中东之行中将重点关注加沙的下一步发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/what-s-next-for-gaza-is-blinken-s-focus-on-new-mideast-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位美国高级官员表示，国务卿安东尼·布林肯将利用自以色列与哈马斯冲突爆发以来的第四次中东之行，重点关注加沙地带的未来治理，同时也寻求遏制以色列与哈马斯冲突的威胁。更广泛的地区战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/what-s-next-for-gaza-is-blinken-s-focus-on-new-mideast-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 20:03:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在反对特朗普时称选票上的民主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-casts-trump-threat-to-democracy-as-central-to-2024-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登拉开了今年的首次竞选活动，他直截了当地向选民表明，他的前任唐纳德·特朗普是民主的威胁，不应该重返白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-casts-trump-threat-to-democracy-as-central-to-2024-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>州政府辩称，特朗普因欺诈欠纽约人 3.7 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/new-york-now-seeks-370-million-from-trump-in-civil-fraud-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州告诉一位法官，最终将对民事欺诈案作出判决，唐纳德·特朗普及其公司应被责令支付 3.7 亿美元，高于 2.5 亿美元，因为十多年来在财务记录中夸大了他的资产价值审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/new-york-now-seeks-370-million-from-trump-in-civil-fraud-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普聘请德克萨斯州堕胎法背后的律师进行最高法院选票斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/trump-ballot-fight-at-supreme-court-led-by-texan-behind-abortion-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州律师设计了该州为期六周的堕胎法，允许普通公民向违法者寻求 10,000 美元的赏金，该律师已被唐纳德·特朗普聘请，帮助他在美国最高法院争取留在总统选票上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/trump-ballot-fight-at-supreme-court-led-by-texan-behind-abortion-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州率先获得从加拿大进口更便宜药品的批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-fda-approves-florida-plan-to-import-drugs-from-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府将允许佛罗里达州从加拿大进口更便宜的处方药，为一项可能刺激其他州效仿的计划开了绿灯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-fda-approves-florida-plan-to-import-drugs-from-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 14:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳税人将面临数十亿的臭氧狂热账单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/ozempic-s-cost-weight-loss-drugs-will-be-billed-to-us-taxpayers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国各地的州和地方政府正在努力解决一个日益严重的问题：治疗糖尿病和肥胖症的昂贵药物可能会耗尽他们的医疗保健预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/ozempic-s-cost-weight-loss-drugs-will-be-billed-to-us-taxpayers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于反对派抵制选举，美国向孟加拉国施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/upcoming-bangladesh-election-puts-democracy-and-us-ties-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国总理谢赫·哈西娜将在周日举行的遭到抵制的选举中延长其 15 年的统治。现在的问题是，以美国为首的西方政府是否会惩罚美国的民主倒退，并拉近其与中国的距离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/upcoming-bangladesh-election-puts-democracy-and-us-ties-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 02:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
